2007-08-20  Jean-David Gadina  <info@macmade.net>

	* Increased API internal version number to 3.1.
	* Fixed a bug in function fe_buildLoginBox method (cHash related problem)
	* New function: fe_typoLinkParams. This function is used to build the additionalParams option of a typoLink from a frontend plugin.
	* New function: fe_linkTP_keepPIvars. Same as tslib_piBase::pi_linkTP_keepPIvars, but with a bugfix for the cHash.
	* New function: fe_linkTP_keepPIvars_url. Same as tslib_piBase::pi_linkTP_keepPIvars_url, but with a bugfix for the cHash.
	* Fixed a bug in method fe_linkTP related to the cHash.

