2006-09-4  Jean-David Gadina  <info@macmade.net>

	* New function: fe_buildSearchBox. This function constructs a standard Typo3 search box for use in plugins. The result is basically the same as tslib_piBase::pi_list_searchBox, but the output is valid XHTML, without tables
	* New function: fe_buildBrowseBox. This function constructs a standard Typo3 browse box for use in plugins. The result is basically the same as tslib_piBase::pi_list_browseresults, but the output is valid XHTML, without tables.

2006-08-22  Jean-David Gadina  <info@macmade.net>

	* Modified the fe_makeStyledContent function. The generated code should now be clean and valid XHTML.

2006-08-22  Jean-David Gadina  <info@macmade.net>

	* Increased API internal version number to 2.7.
	* Modified the fe_buildSwapClassesJSCode function. The generated JavaScript is now able to change an otionnal icon, at the same time as the class name.

2006-06-07  Jean-David Gadina  <info@macmade.net>

	* Added parameter 'checkType' to function div_checkArrayKeys. That parameter is used to check the variable type of the final array.
	* Updated the API documentation (doc/manual.sxw).
	* Release of version 2.6 of the API.

2006-06-06  Jean-David Gadina  <info@macmade.net>

	* Increased API internal version number to 2.6.
	* New function: div_isType. The function is used to check the type of a variable, without using the PHP gettype() function, which should never be used to check a variable type.

