2005-10-06  Jean-David Gadina  <info@macmade.net>

	* Fixed a bug with the function div_array2xml, which would prevent the numeric tags to be processed correctly.
	* New function: fe_linkTP. The function is used to create a link to a page. It's the same function as tslib_pibase::pi_linkTP, except that a configuration array for the typolink can be passed directly as an argument.

2005-09-12  Jean-David Gadina  <info@macmade.net>

