2005-09-05  Jean-David Gadina  <info@macmade.net>

	* New function: div_vCardFileParse. The function is used to parse a vCard file and to return its content as a multidimensionnal array.
	* New function: div_convertLineBreaks. The function is used to convert different line breaks into standard Unix line breaks.

