2005-04-22  Jean-David Gadina  <info@macmade.net>

	* Added a change log (CVS compliant)
	* Increased API internal version number to 1.5.
	* New function: div_formatXHTML. The function is used to format XHTML compliant code, with line breaks and indentations.
	* Modified the div_xml2array function to allow the use of same multiple tag names inside the same parent element. In that case, the array keys are now suffixed with a '-N', where N is the current occurence number of the tag name.
	* Modified the div_array2xml function to add compatibility with the modified div_xml2array function (see previous entry).
	* Corrected some API functions' descriptions.
	* Added the $funcId internal variable to some functions.
	* Changed the name of the 'MAIN' section to 'INTERNAL'.
	* Fixed a bug with the function div_xml2array, which would prevent the tag attributes to be stored in some cases.
	* Modified the div_array2xml function to add compatibility with the modified div_xml2array function (see previous entry).
	* Updated the class index.
	* Added a copy of the GNU General Public License in the distribution of the API (GPL.txt).
